      <title>负债不断增加，沃尔格林和 VillageMD 聘请顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/walgreens-villagemd-taps-advisers-as-backer-pursues-exit-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沃博联医疗集团 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 正在向 Perella Weinberg Partners 和 AlixPartners 寻求建议，以帮助其改善与健康诊所业务 VillageMD 相关的运营和资产负债表。]]></description>
